00:13:24,435 --> 00:13:27,798
wrote some cool eye and skin shaders and lighting tweaks,

262
00:13:27,818 --> 00:13:29,919
such as being able to procedurally generate shadows

263
00:13:30,980 --> 00:13:33,002
from eyelids and using bent normal maps

264
00:13:33,022 --> 00:13:34,863
to remove lighting artifacts.

